# Angular-only guardrail

This repository is **Angular-only**. All application code lives at the repo root under `src/app/`.

## Required

- Implement UI, features, fixes, and Figma-driven work under `src/app/`.
- Use **Angular 18** standalone components (no NgModules), Angular Router, and Signals where the codebase already does.
- Reuse existing layout (`app-shell`, `nav-sidebar`), services, models, and design tokens in `src/styles.scss` and `tailwind.config.js`.
- Preserve stable `data-testid` attributes on interactive elements when adding or changing UI.

## Forbidden

- Do **not** add React, Vue, or other frontend frameworks.
- Do **not** introduce Vite/shadcn/Radix UI patterns from legacy Replit exports.
- Do **not** scatter mock data inside UI components — use services and fixtures.

## When the user shares Figma or screenshots

- Map designs to the matching **Angular** page under `src/app/pages/`.
- Create or update `.component.ts` / `.component.html` (and scoped styles if needed).

## Backend / API

- The only server in this repo is `server/index.mjs` (USPS address proxy for dev).
- UI still belongs in Angular; touch the proxy only when an API contract change is required.
